        <p>There were also some slightly more subjective measurements. I took into consideration factors like the total game attendance, as I generally believe more fans at a game makes the game more exciting. I also gave games a penalty as they became more meaningless to the final standings of the league. For example, a game between two 50-100 teams at the end of the season will incur a drastic increase to its boring store due to the lack of importance of the game to the season. All the factors and their effects on the boring score can be seen in the GitHub repository for the project.</p>
