        <p>I am going to give the most boring game award to the Angels at Athletics game though. Despite not having the highest score, it has everything you could ever ask for when it comes to the ideal boring game. A game between two terrible teams playing at this point for almost nothing. A mostly empty Oakland stadium. 10 pitchers used despite being a shutout game. A 5-0 final score with only eight hits the entire game, with the A’s getting an early lead they kept throughout. And most importantly, absolutely no notable stats from either team coming out of this game. There is really nothing to talk about when analyzing this game, and that is why it is so perfect.</p>
